"The new model allows Cloudflare to block residential proxy traffic while allowing benign residential users to visit Cloudflare-protected websites from the same residential network.",
"ML v8 is currently being tested in shadow mode and is classifying more than 17 million unique IPs that participate in residential proxy attacks every hour."
]
},
{
"paragraphs": [
"The article provides case studies demonstrating the effectiveness of ML v8 in detecting previously missed attacks. In one case, v8 was able to correctly classify 95% of requests from distributed residential proxy attacks targeting a customer's website.",
"In another case, the new model successfully detected a previously missed content scraping attack evident by increased detection during traffic spikes."
]
},
{
"paragraphs": [
"The article also discusses improvements in detecting bots from cloud providers. Early results show that v8 detects 20% more bots from cloud providers, with up to 70% more bots detected on zones that are marked as 'under attack'."
]
},
