        },
        {
          "text": "- Create a new index specifically for Query Suggestions"
        },
        {
          "text": "- Configure options, including tools to ban inappropriate suggestions and decide how many results are needed for a suggestion"
        },
        {
          "text": "- Once the index builds itself, display the data it sends to the frontend"
        },
        {
          "text": "Here's an example of JavaScript code that connects Autocomplete with the Query Suggestions index:"
